{"tid":28142,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[屯元天]召喚所有想踩Roller既面孔","createTime":"2016-12-07T18:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T18:26:50.000Z","uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b380fe17ed30d7b07bd1f0f8966aa7894afa4b90","tid":28142,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:17:31.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人有興趣踩ROLLER/一直都有踩 只不過以前屯門區搵唔到人踩而迫不得已去其他地方搵人踩呢?<br />\r\n<br />\r\n可能以前係咁 但係而家你絕不孤單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n我以前都係成日一個人玩 因為完全搵唔到志同道合既人<br />\r\n但係當我每日無間斷都落去玩既時候 開始識到一班踩ROLLER既人<br />\r\n根住我地自己再開左個ROLLER GROUP<br />\r\n一開始只係得小貓三四隻 但係而家係我們大家既努力之下已經不斷壯大<br />\r\n唔同時段 只要唔落雨都好大機會搵到人踩<br />\r\n<br />\r\n如果你係住屯門 而因為返工/學業或者其他因素覺得出去周圍踩好麻煩既話 歡迎你加入我地<br />\r\n因為屯門人而家再不孤單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n我地係一班業餘而且對ROLLER有熱誠既人<br />\r\n簡單D黎講即係業餘發燒友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n每晚係個埸到傾下計 HEA下 周圍踩吹下風 去食下野<br />\r\n所以我地唔會有架子 唔會SELL你地買野 唔會SELL你地入班<br />\r\n只要你肯學 我地肯教 只不過唔係好專業 但係足夠你踩街跑街<br />\r\n係我地個GROUP到既人好多一開始都係新手 我親眼睇住佢地不斷進步<br />\r\n由一開始只係兩三條友踩街 到而家最多有十六七個人一齊踩<br />\r\n亦都歡迎各種模式既玩法 大家可以一齊交流下<br />\r\n暫時平花剎車跳同踩街都各有人玩 另外亦都有定期既踩街團 係香港周圍踩<br />\r\n<br />\r\n有興趣既請PM我留低你既電話+點叫你 我會加你入我地既GROUP<br />\r\n希望係真心玩 而唔係當我地個GROUP係5P交友GROUP 呢類人會直接踢<br />\r\n同埋加完唔出黎玩/係咁賣廣告既煩膠一樣會踢<br />\r\n<br />\r\n亦都歡迎其他區既人有興趣一齊黎玩下 因為最近都加左唔少天水圍既人<br />\r\n大家都玩得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n如果你有朋友係住屯門又或者屯門附近<br />\r\n而又自己玩緊/覺得周圍去好煩<br />\r\n希望你可以比呢個POST佢睇 考慮黎唔黎JOIN我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n因為見到最近有D流浪ROLLER友 如果想既話歡迎黎一齊玩<br />\r\n不過想自己一兩個FD玩都冇所謂 如果想JOIN就直接踩入黎啦<br />\r\n想學野我地會教你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n\r<br />\n我地每個星期五晚只要天氣好既話都會有聚會 時間大約係九點半左右"},{"pid":"5b28cbb6a1360f8bc198dd81c2357d11ed8027b2","tid":28142,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:18:13.000Z","msg":"Q&amp;A<br />\r\n<br />\r\nQ: ROLLER係咪有好多種唔同玩法?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA: 無錯 ROLLER除左就咁勁踩之外仲有好多玩法<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FEnOPFQlD9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFEnOPFQlD9A&d=kSdeLN%2FdCW%2Frwl4ScOuxTnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=5876aba1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FEnOPFQlD9A</a> 呢種係X-GAME 定極限<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CWor7T9NUOE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCWor7T9NUOE&d=kSdeLN%2FdCW%2Frwl4ScOuxTnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=2e2bd666\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CWor7T9NUOE</a> 呢種係花式過樁(Slalom)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7qDqh-wvElc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7qDqh-wvElc&d=kSdeLN%2FdCW%2Frwl4ScOuxTnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=8541da2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7qDqh-wvElc</a> 呢種係花式剎車 (Slide)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cojSRhxA2-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcojSRhxA2-4&d=kSdeLN%2FdCW%2Frwl4ScOuxTnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=dc16e6aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cojSRhxA2-4</a> 踩街都可以踩得好型<br />\r\n<br />\r\nQ: 如果我想學花式既話應該去邊到?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA: 基本上上面既片簡單既花式我地都可以教到你(例如簡單既平花 踩街既跳轉180度/360度) 所以如果你不求專業 只係業餘興趣間唔中先會玩下既可以JOIN我地 簡單既平花我地都有幾個人練緊 我自己本身玩開剎車不過練到悶悶地都開始練平花 有興趣可以黎一齊學或者高手黎指教下我地呢班新人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n剎車方面因為香港冇咩人玩 而小弟亦都好不幸既鐘意玩呢樣野 所以都好努力學緊 如果搵唔到人教你既話歡迎黎搵我教你 或者另外約個時間出黎一齊交流下 剎車方面如果我地都教你唔到你就要返大陸學了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nQ: 玩ROLLER危唔危險架?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA: 其他唔危險 只要你戴足護具( 護手 護膝 護肘) 如果你仲係驚死既可以戴埋頭盔同籃球果種防跌褲 咁樣你想傷都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nQ: 如果有時我想自己玩既話應該如何入手?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA: 呢段鬼佬片有齊哂咁多基本野 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L8Gs_eyIPFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DL8Gs_eyIPFA&d=kSdeLN%2FdCW%2Frwl4ScOuxTnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=d21bd5d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L8Gs_eyIPFA</a> 如果你黎問既話我地可以親自示範比你睇同直接教你"},{"pid":"72a160f4add18b24c78b29e53213b748f16f24cd","tid":28142,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:19:11.000Z","msg":"Q: ROLLER係咪廢青夜青先會玩?因為比我既印象唔太好<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA: 我地有D人會食煙 講粗口 但係人品唔會差得去邊 各行各業既人都有<br />\r\n有裝修佬 文員仔 打政府工既人 炒散 中學生 大學生等等 或者我地唔係返咩專業既工 但係對於一樣業餘既興趣黎講呢樣野我覺得唔太重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nQ: 踩ROLLER係咪冇可能係街到踩既呢?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA: 絕對踩到 正如上面條片一樣 我地有時候都會周圍街 不過有D技巧一定要學 例如T剎 轉彎等等 令到你同埋其他行人可以安全D<br />\r\n雖然香港又窄又多人 但係我地主要係夜晚踩 所以人都唔會多得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nQ: 你地會唔會好小圈子?又或者排斥其他人?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA: 如果你係肯踩肯學就一定可以融入到我地 如果少出聲果D我地都會盡量去R下水吹 只不過我自己係真毒向左走向右走 所以有時都唔係好敢去R水吹<br />\r\n<br />\r\n如果有興趣既歡迎所有人黎一齊玩 我地每個星期五晚都會有聚會 我通常都會去練SLIDE 都有人練平花 歡迎你黎一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n有其他關於ROLLER方面既問題都可以係到問 我會盡量答你<br />\r\n有興趣一齊既就PM我你既電話<br />\r\n唔想比電話可以直接星期五晚一齊黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nQ: 如果我要買鞋應該去邊到?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA: 係淘寶買最平四五百就有交易 鞋碼方面好少會比錯 最多只會錯色<br />\r\n如果你唔放心就可以係pro skate買 因為可以試鞋 岩心水先買<br />\r\n最後都係睇你自己點簡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a46141dae8028b14601c7a6b8b086af913973cf","tid":28142,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fsbVd8V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfsbVd8V.jpg&h=6acb4d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n點去ROLLER埸?<br />\r\n<br />\r\n屯門西鐵站B出口(輕鐵屯門站)<br />\r\n下面會有一條單車徑<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/mHkWRiP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmHkWRiP.jpg&h=5fcf6f73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n之後一路行到盡頭就會見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n認到條單車徑就可以一路行到 幾方便下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8a2f9b90ad3891e410b841dcc202f8268ae021","tid":28142,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:21:11.000Z","msg":"我地自己既PAGE: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tmrollerskating?ref=hl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftmrollerskating%3Fref%3Dhl&d=kSdeLN%2FdCW%2Frwl4ScOuxTnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=32b32a59\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tmrollerskating?ref=hl</a><br />\r\n第一條宣傳片: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6SpoQujOZHg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6SpoQujOZHg&d=kSdeLN%2FdCW%2Frwl4ScOuxTnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=0c985e51\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6SpoQujOZHg</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n落手落腳拍比起想像中難好多 所以有好多改善既空間<br />\r\n不過我地會努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該係呢年會再拍多一條<br />\r\n<br />\r\n自家出品既中級剎車片<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t1C_wx1TiTk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dt1C_wx1TiTk&d=kSdeLN%2FdCW%2Frwl4ScOuxTnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=0e8b266a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t1C_wx1TiTk</a> C級 花式剎車-Savanna<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ue18Dcxsjk0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Due18Dcxsjk0&d=kSdeLN%2FdCW%2Frwl4ScOuxTnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=db2bbab3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ue18Dcxsjk0</a> C級 花式剎車-Acid Toe Wheeling<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hKNM3J7hy6Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhKNM3J7hy6Q&d=kSdeLN%2FdCW%2Frwl4ScOuxTnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=429e60ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hKNM3J7hy6Q</a> B級 花式剎車-Toe Toe Unity<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b9cTI9_2umY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Db9cTI9_2umY&d=kSdeLN%2FdCW%2Frwl4ScOuxTnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=c44497e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b9cTI9_2umY</a>   A級 花式剎車-Toe Toe Cross Parallel <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8TTVgobKYQk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8TTVgobKYQk&d=kSdeLN%2FdCW%2Frwl4ScOuxTnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=5394258b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8TTVgobKYQk</a> B級 花式剎車-Back Slide <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MaURt59TmNs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMaURt59TmNs&d=kSdeLN%2FdCW%2Frwl4ScOuxTnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=ec6acd92\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MaURt59TmNs</a> A級 花式剎車-變態恩歲<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rI69dqKTGWk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrI69dqKTGWk&d=kSdeLN%2FdCW%2Frwl4ScOuxTnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=b4d27030\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rI69dqKTGWk</a> 輕鬆片<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mye2IyUoQI8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dmye2IyUoQI8&d=kSdeLN%2FdCW%2Frwl4ScOuxTnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=ad9ae62d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mye2IyUoQI8</a>  輕鬆片<br />\r\n<br />\r\n都係d剎程普通既花式 之前去左維園roller埸玩興起拍左幾段<br />\r\n之後會再拍多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n有咩問題PM問又得 呢到問又得 係PAGE PM我地都得 (想睇本土出產既剎車片可以留名叫我地試一試 不過有好多都唔得 因為我地唔識 來來去去都係果幾招扮叉燒仔) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\nCD ROM可以係FB PAGE到PM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375c224c9e8da2ecf3c6ec5eb5868d2caf57dcb1","tid":28142,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:21:49.000Z","msg":"如果有家長想搵人教下自己既仔女玩ROLLER<br />\r\n或者團體/學校有興趣搞個ROLLER興趣班都可以聯絡我<br />\r\n我可以每個星期抽一兩個鐘唔收錢免費教 因為我自己仲讀緊書同每星期有幾晚要固定去練習 所以時間唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n另外我地亦都可以幫你地訂埋鞋/成套裝備 比唔同地方同鋪頭既價你地參考 唔會抽水 (因為有FD搞開呢D 所以要買好方便 當然緊係要你地自己比返錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"dfe9185ec41bcbf39fc33a435c2609b1eb2cc661","tid":28142,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0608c5330d189597a20627bf77b9bd90251d10b8","tid":28142,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51399a8e46f241d35c303473b116161bdab075b0","tid":28142,"uid":14826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:36:02.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"9b461dec50ec52082ef167fb664c770c67e3f40a","tid":28142,"uid":2